Description: Change default editor from nano to /usr/bin/editor
 GitHub CLI gh sets nano as the default editor.  However, as per
 Debian Policy ยง11.4, the default editor should be /usr/bin/editor,
 not nano.  Thanks to Jakub Wilk for the bug report.
Author: Anthony Fok <foka@debian.org>
Origin: vendor
Bug-Debian: https://bugs.debian.org/1008761
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2022-05-31, 2022-09-05
---
This patch header follows DEP-3: http://dep.debian.net/deps/dep3/
--- a/pkg/surveyext/editor.go
+++ b/pkg/surveyext/editor.go
@@ -28,6 +28,8 @@
 		defaultEditor = e
 	} else if runtime.GOOS == "windows" {
 		defaultEditor = "notepad"
+	} else {
+		defaultEditor = "/usr/bin/editor" // As per Debian Policy ยง11.4
 	}
 }
 
